      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Periodical\" title=\"Periodical\">Periodical</a> * ChessBits</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:224px;\"><a href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/marcus.htm\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/9/92/Cb-logo2.gif\" width=\"222\" height=\"222\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Cb-logo2.gif\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>ChessBits <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>ChessBits</b>,<br />\nwas a German computer chess periodical, first released in 1999 by <a href=\"/Marcus_K%C3%A4stner\" title=\"Marcus Kästner\">Marcus Kästner</a>. 21 issues were released until 2003, when the unexpected death of Marcus later partner and co-editor <a href=\"/Detlef_Pordzik\" title=\"Detlef Pordzik\">Detlef Pordzik</a> was the main reason ChessBits was discontinued. \n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Selected_Articles\">Selected Articles</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessBits&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Selected Articles\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a href=\"/Marcus_K%C3%A4stner\" title=\"Marcus Kästner\">Marcus Kästner</a> (<b>2000</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.rebel.nl/marcus.htm\">Interview with Ed Schröder</a></i>. ChessBits, No. 8, hosted by <a href=\"/Ed_Schroder\" title=\"Ed Schroder\">Ed Schröder</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/index.php?title=Alwin_Gruber&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1\" class=\"new\" title=\"Alwin Gruber (page does not exist)\">Alwin Gruber</a> (<b>2001</b>). <i>Schachcomputer die Geschichte schrieben - Der Novag Savant</i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">ChessBits</a>, 01-2001, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.schaakcomputers.nl/hein_veldhuis/database/files/09-1982%20%5BJ-1001%5D%20Novag%20-%20Savant%20II.pdf\">pdf</a> hosted and slightly modified by <a href=\"/Hein_Veldhuis\" title=\"Hein Veldhuis\">Hein Veldhuis</a>&#160;» <a href=\"/Savant\" title=\"Savant\">Savant</a></li>\n<li> <a href=\"/Detlef_Pordzik\" title=\"Detlef Pordzik\">Detlef Pordzik</a> (<b>2002</b>). <i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.schach-niggemann.com/seiten/chebit19/files/excalibur.htm\">Ein Brettcomputer im Königsformat -  Der Excalibur Grandmaster</a></i>. <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">ChessBits</a>, No. 19 (German), hosted by <a href=\"/Schachversand_Niggemann\" title=\"Schachversand Niggemann\">Schachversand Niggemann</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessBits&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.schachversand.de/startseite.html?Seite=d/listen/kategorien/U1_103.html\">Magazines ChessBits</a> from <a href=\"/Schachversand_Niggemann\" title=\"Schachversand Niggemann\">Schachversand Niggemann</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=ChessBits&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a href=\"/Marcus_K%C3%A4stner\" title=\"Marcus Kästner\">